messages.message: @Seb - Have added you to CDD ILE repo on NW env. You will find your encryption solutions under Users > Seb

Thanks Aimé, I’ll review these today to make sure it works properly. V1.1 is on its way, I’ve  added a standalone encrypt_ib_file.py for the case users need to encrypt files from AWS S3 to transfer back to IB. I’ve tidied up the code so that its core library can be easily packaged as a dev ex toolkit(I’m thinking about ib_easy_cryptography as a name). I’ll demonstrate this during a knowledge sharing session next week that Saikat asked me to do.
NICE! Just let me know if you want me to send anything else across to NW env
